OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAn unsettled
OL,6,Fevening with showers and thunderstorms
OL,7,Flikely. Turning more settled overnight
OL,8,Fand some breaks in the cloud
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Temperatures remaining
OL,10,Fwarm overnight with light
OL,11,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,14,Fto all parts through Sunday. Cloudy at
OL,15,Ftimes with some sunny intervals during
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Winds moderate
OL,17,Fsouthwesterly, breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
